{"tid":56252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京衛計委說毒霧有益健康！","createTime":"2016-12-27T06:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T13:49:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"866bd904a9984bb9ef4e01496d679802535ae9f5","tid":56252,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:01:04.000Z","msg":"隨著北京霧霾不斷加重，一家瑞典抗生素耐藥性研究機構近日發表最新報告稱，在北京的空氣中發現了碳青霉烯類抗生素的耐藥性基因。北京市衛計委就此作出公開回應，稱耐藥性的增加不意味著致病性的增強。而且空氣中存在的大多數細菌或真菌對人體是無害的，甚至有些細菌是有益的。<br />\n<br />\n北京雾霾现耐药菌？专家：对人无害<br />\n<a href=\"http://epaper.bjnews.com.cn/html/2016-11/26/content_661733.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fepaper.bjnews.com.cn%2Fhtml%2F2016-11%2F26%2Fcontent_661733.htm&d=Odt83XHNhBZYezGTnddDE3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a4a7ff9f\" target=\"_blank\">http://epaper.bjnews.com.cn/html/2016-11/26/content_661733.htm</a><br />\n国外研究称北京雾霾含耐药菌；市卫计委援引专家说法，细菌耐药性的增加不意味着致病性增强"},{"pid":"a9f9601ad1fa969bf9ae259fea69ae48a4226a1a","tid":56252,"uid":42299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5ce5f10f5f7e13e8aaf973ff12cd761ab4d270","tid":56252,"uid":21356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:04:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 毒霧有益健康  中國或成最大贏家"},{"pid":"befda54d7464e59795baeabdb4a0aff3ba8ab785","tid":56252,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T06:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"